there are three types of Recommender system
1. content based:  the recommendations are made based on the similarity between the content or attributes of the items.
2. collaborative filtering:Collaborative recommendation is a method of recommendation that suggests items to users based on the preferences and behaviors of other like users.
3. hybrid (uses both system)

outline:
data
preprocessing
model
deployment into website

1. preprocessing
remove all the unusefull columns
convert the list of dictionaries into tags
merging the tags to make a whole paragraph

2.how to design a model

converting the text into vector called text vectorization.
do the stemming
euclidean distance(tip to tip) and cosine distance(angle)
euclidean distance fail in high dimensional data
